# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# GENERATED ARTIFACT POLICY
#
# COMMITTED (canonical snapshots — changes tracked in git):
#   05_MATTERS/DASHBOARDS/   — daily matter + inbox digest snapshots
#   05_MATTERS/MATTER_REGISTRY.md — hand-maintained registry (edit directly)
#   05_MATTERS/INDEX.md      — ML1-gated index (ML1 instruction required)
#   06_RUNS/ops/MATTER_TODO_REPORT.md — committed weekly report
#   06_RUNS/ops/MATTER_TODO_LEDGER.json — committed ledger (human-editable)
#   04_INITIATIVES/LL_PORTFOLIO/CHIEF_OF_STAFF/ — portfolio briefs
#
# IGNORED (ephemeral run artifacts — never commit):
#   06_RUNS/RUN-*/           — timestamped run output directories
#   06_RUNS/state/           — runtime state (rebuilt on each run)
#   06_RUNS/logs/            — append-only audit logs
#   06_RUNS/ops/gmail_fetch_latest.json — per-run email cache
#   cache/*.json             — Clio/Gmail/SharePoint cache files
#   tokens.json, oauth_state.json — Google OAuth tokens
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Runtime artifacts
state/
06_RUNS/state/
06_RUNS/RUN-*/
06_RUNS/ops/gmail_fetch_latest.json
cache/*.json
tokens.json
oauth_state.json

# Google OAuth secrets
config/google_oauth_client.json
config/*token*.json
